# Folex Lite Astro – Free Astro Theme for Startups & Agencies

Folex Lite Astro is a minimalist, fast, and SEO-friendly starter theme built with Astro 5 and Tailwind CSS. Perfect for startups, digital agencies, and personal projects, it provides a solid foundation to build your site with ease.

## Features

* Clean, minimal design with fast performance
* SEO-optimized and accessibility-ready
* Multilingual support (i18n)
* Customizable design tokens (colors, fonts, spacing)
* Global content and navigation via Markdown & json
* Contact form included  
* Easy deployment to Vercel, Netlify, or Cloudflare Pages  
* Markdown-powered content system  
* Commercial & Personal Usage License and open source  
